</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCC36874057F865FE9D91124026BC80" blockId="4.[264,1323,284,390]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Gonocoxite simple, mat, densely sculptured; apex truncated. Gonostylus narrow, blade shaped and apically tapered without process or notable pilosity. Penis valve blade shaped, dorsal side very narrow. Volsella differentiated, large and bud shaped.</paragraph>
